    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order of large number of widely distributed, shallow-water cephalopods having eight sucker-bearing arms or tentacles, a beak-like mouth, and either only a vestigial internal shell or no shell at all.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
